parameters:
\SE[77]This is... the sea!? \SE[12]The sand that looks like
jewels, the waves that ebb and flow... \SE[17]I can't
believe such a place really exists...!

\SE[21]Oh, you're so adorable when you're excited...
\!\SE[0]You said you wanted to come here. \.So, how is it?
\.Is it fun...?

\SE[39]Yes, it's amazing...! \SE[59]I heard that the water
level of the sea changes depending on the time. \SE[55]I
wonder why that happens, it's so mysterious...

\SE\SE[0]At night, the moon comes out, right? \SE[0]The
force that pulls around that star... It's the gravitational
force that lifts the water of the sea.
\SE[70]That much power exists in the distant moon...!?

\SE[15]It's mysterious, isn't it...? \!\SE[1]That's why when
the moon gets closer at night, the water level rises, and it
weakens and the water level drops when it sets in the
morning.

\SE[71]The 'moon' is amazing...! \SE[66]Lunaroa, how do you
know about that...?

\SE[46]Did you think it was amazing...? Are you falling in
love all over again? \SE[45]Then, say I love you?

\SE[52]I-I feel like it's been a while since I've
experienced something like this...! \SE[65]I think I might
need some rehabilitation...!!
\SE[59]No way...! \SE[23]Just one more step, keep going...!

\SE[14]There was a good food stall! It seems to be a popular
shop in this area! \SE[0]I'm sure Lady Lunaroa will be
satisfied!

\SE[16]Hey, Tita! It's still my time now, right? \SE[12]It's
not fair to interrupt...!

\SE[14]That time ended while Laura was fidgeting! My time
has already begun! \SE[13]The current Laura is a
nuisance...!

\SE[64]I, who is your lover, am a nuisance...!? \SE[24]No
way, no way...!!

\SE[20] (I'm happy about everyone's 'good intentions', but
this situation is troublesome...)

\SE[14]Ah!? They're doing something happy without me!
Unfair!! They should do it where I can see!!

\SE[54]How can you continue without getting bored...
\!\SE[3]Being lovey-dovey all the time, I don't really
understand.

\SE[14]You're the one who's mostly like that! Acting like a
baby and calling out Mama at your age...! \SE[13]Hurry up
and wean yourself off breast milk!

\SE[16]W-Weaning...!? \!\SE[15]How rude! That's not how it
is between me and Mama! \!\SE[12]It's something more noble,
irreplaceable...!

\SE[15]Hmm hmm, they're so close, so close... This is also a
form of happiness.... \SE[16]Hmm hmm, diversity,
diversity...

\SE[56] (It's become so lively all of a sudden, it's hard to
believe...)

\SE[51]P-Please, let's not fight... \SE[1]Um, so there's a
good shop, right? I wonder what kind of place it is?
\SE[20]I-I'm curious...

\SE[14]Kakigori! It's shaved ice!! \SE[13]They shave the ice
into fine, crunchy pieces and then pour your favorite syrup
on top to eat it!

\SE[4]Eating kakigori in the hot weather is apparently
irresistible! \SE[0]The syrup is also colorful and very
beautiful!

\SE[6]Huh, is that all? Paying money for something as simple
as freezing water and pouring sugar on it? Are you stupid?

\SE[14]Just freezing water and pouring sugar on it...!? How
dare you say that in front of Lady Lunaroa, you...!!
\SE[13]Because you don't understand this elegance, you'll
always be a child!

\SE[4]Well, isn't it bad if we don't line up soon?
\SE[3]There's a long queue forming at the entrance of the
shop.

\SE[14]W-What did you say...!? \SE[13]I can't stay here
doing something like this! I have to go...!

\SE[12]One person, up to two...!? Oh no...! With just that,
I won't be able to satisfy Lady Lunaroa...!!

\SE[12]Alice! Claudia!! Come on, help me!! \SE[14]You two
also need to line up...! Hurry up!!
\SE[4]A queue, huh... \!\SE[3]Is that a happy thing?

\SE[14]Of course...! A queue is the manifestation of humans
seeking happiness! \SE[13]In fact, you could say that it is
happiness itself...!
\SE[2]I see... \!\SE[15]Well then, I'll help you out.

\SE[14]Look, Claudia too!! \!\SE[13]If we don't hurry, the
next person will come...!!

\SE[16]No way! Why do I have to do something like that...!?
\SE[15]

\SE[14]Why not...!? Don't you want to see the happy face of
Mama!? \SE[13]Even though we're indebted to her, don't you
want to show filial piety...!?
\SE[56]W-Well, Mama wants to... try eating... shaved ice...?

\SE[16]Yes, very much. \!\SE[0]If I could eat it together
with everyone... \.I would be very happy....

\SE[46]Yes, that's right... \!\SE[38]I've had some tough
experiences, so I can be a bit timid and easily
misunderstood...

\SE[47]Kind and caring... \SE[45]I'm sure I'm still not used
to expressing my affection. \SE[21]That's really... all
there is to it.

\SE[46]So, if it's desired... I thought I would become Mama
for you. \SE[20]...Even though we haven't even gotten
married yet.

\SE[56]If Lunaroa wants to do that... \SE[55]I will go along
with it.

\SE[46]Thank you... Laura. \SE[15]Thank you for putting up
with my selfishness...

\SE[45]Somehow, I've become really confused....
\SE[59]Everyone I've met so far... There hasn't been a
single bad person....

\SE[23]Everyone is just trying their best to make things
better. \!\SE[18]And sometimes, they end up hurting those
around them.... \!\SE[59]But somehow, I can't bring myself
to dislike them....

\SE[23]It's not Alice, but... \SE[56]At least, I hope that
the people who stay by my side... \SE[56]Can all be happy.

\SE[64]W-What am I saying, acting like a child...
\!\SE[29]I'm starting to feel a little embarrassed...

\SE[46]That's not true.... \SE[45]I feel like Laura has
grown up too....

\SE[56]In exchange for listening to Lunaroa's selfishness...
Can you also listen to my selfishness?

\SE[38]The time we couldn't meet... I want you to make up
for it. \SE[55]For all the time I was lonely...

\SE[46]Oh...? A selfish request from a grown-up has come....
\SE[55]But is it okay to ask for something like that? If so,
then maybe tonight...

\SE[28]I-I... I'm... stupid.... \!\SE[60]That's not what I
meant....

There have been various things... I've cried a lot, laughed
a lot... There have been scary people... But more than that,
there have been kind people too...

I am very clumsy.... I might not have been able to do it
well. There were times when I lamented my own
incompetence....

I... I'm glad... that I love you. I'm glad... that I can be
by your side.
\SE[2]I was here. \!\SE[0]I searched all over town...

\SE[92]Tita... I'm sorry. \SE[90]I just wanted to change my
mood a little...

\SE[37]You don't have to apologize, it's fine.
\SE[48]Laura... you did your best, right...?

\SE[37]And besides, I... I can't fight like everyone else...
I can't use magic... \SE[48]I don't have the right to blame
anyone.

\SE[32]That's why... I was frustrated. \SE[47]I couldn't
fight together with Laura and the others... \SE[8]I couldn't
be of any use to Lady Lunaroa...

\SE[12]So please... promise me, Laura. \SE[13]Please, make
sure to save Lady Lunaroa... \SE[14]While you're not here, I
will protect Lady Lunaroa. \SE[13]No matter how long it
takes, I won't give up either.

\SE[33]And besides... I'm sure... the only one who can save
her is you. \SE[2] But even so, if... you don't have enough
power...

\SE[44]I understand... I promise. \SE[102]No matter what
happens, I will never give up.

Moving to the Second Part. \!To return to the title screen,
\.please make sure to Save without fail.
